		{
			dependencies: ["4CCBE98B5628C77A"]
			description: [
				"Immersive Engineering wires can transfer more energy, but have a downside: &othey will damage you if you will be close to them.&r What else you expected from powered wires? "
				""
				"To transfer energy now you need to use Wire Connectors on blocks that give and recieve energy, and Wire Relays to transfer it between points of interest."
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"IE wires have energy loss. Every 16 blocks they will loose 5% of overal energy pool. Additional loss happen if you will not use full wires carrying capacity."
				""
				"LV connectors can input or output max 256 FE to the wires. By combining many connectors into single wire through relays the energy loss can be mitigated. &oLV wires max transfer capacity is 2048 FE/t, going higher will burn your wires.&r"
