		{
			dependencies: ["69DB58E1CD20ED2B"]
			description: [
				"With help of small connector you can transfer energy around your base. Unfortunately simplicity comes with a cost: Small connectors don't have any power loss, but can't be too far away for each other. Connectors need to be max 4 blocks from each other and can't support more than 4 connections on one."
				""
				"Not bad for small starter base, but really will not fit huge industrial production."
				""
				"Connectors will only get maximum of 64 FE/t from energy sources and give 256 FE/t on receiving end. They will change behaviour automaticaly if there input or output, but if this didn't happen connectors can be configurate by any wrench to push, pull or do nothing."
